{
  "texts": [
    "MNIST's input was reduced to 320 units and normalized pixel values were rounded off to 0 or 1 to simulate the CA's input.",
    "Though digital, this process merely digitized input, not weights or CA procedures.",
    "The device array utilizes experimental weights adjusted to match its conductance and input current scales.",
    "This ensures the CA computes using genuine analog values.",
    "To elaborate on the learning process, the reduced input of 320 was chunked into groups of 10 and fed to a three-line array."
  ]
}